#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This folder contains only one file, world.desktop. This file is a "
#| "description of the content of the skin. It is used to describe the "
#| "organization of the world and how to display it. You don't have to fill "
#| "it manualy as it will be handled by the &kappname;. But, for the sake of "
